title: Bug 121170 - get column label from meta data object should return user recognizable strings
description: When retrieving column labels from the meta data object, the labels returned before extraction are null. However, after extraction, recognizable strings are obtained.
OB: Before extraction, the labels returned are null.
EB: After extraction, the labels should be recognizable strings.
SR:
To reproduce the issue: 
1. Retrieve the column labels from the meta data object.
2. Check if the labels are null before extraction.
